<br>
<br>Maximum 26 years as on 30th June, 2011 for the general category candidates. Age relaxation for OBC (Non Creamy Layer)/SC/ST/PH candidates will be applicable as per the Presidential Directive. 
	<br><asp:HyperLink ID="HyperLink3" runat="server" Text="Click here to discuss" NavigateUrl="~/interviews-jobs/government-jobs/vacancies_indian_oil_coorporation-iocl-2011.aspx"></asp:HyperLink>
